	PR fortran/26039
	expr.c (gfc_check_conformance):  Reorder error message
	to avoid plural.
	check.c(gfc_check_minloc_maxloc):  Call gfc_check_conformance
	for checking arguments array and mask.
	(check_reduction):  Likewise.

